original: Lundblad, Sven Natanael, kapten, avdelningschef, Göteborg, f. 28/8/95 i Synnerby, Skarab. 1., av August L. o. Augusta Lindkvist. G. m. Ragnie Ziegler. Barn: Monika f. 40, Michael 42, Peter 46. — Stud:ex. i Skara 13, Gci 22. Fänrik i Göta art :reg. 15, löjtn. 19, kapt. i reg. 30, på överg:stat 28. Anst. i Försäkr. A-B Nornan 28, avd:chef där sed. 30. Hobby; ischack. RSO.
translated: Lundblad, Sven Natanael, Captain, Department Manager, Gothenburg, b. August 28, 1895 in Synnerby, Skarab. 1., son of August L. and Augusta Lindkvist. Married to Ragnie Ziegler in the year 19xx. Children: Monika b. 1940, Michael b. 1942, Peter b. 1946. Completed high school in Skara in 1913, and graduated from Gci in 1922. Enlisted as an Ensign in Göta Artillery Regiment 15, promoted to Lieutenant in 1919, became Captain in Regiment 30, transferred to reserve service in 1928. Employed at Insurance Company Nornan AB in 1928, became Department Manager there in 1930. Hobby: ice hockey. Awarded Royal Order of the Seraphim (RSO).
